{"index": 725, "title": "Founding Engineer (\u00a370k-\u00a3100k + Equity) At Getjelly.co.uk", "job_location": "Greater London, England, United Kingdom", "jd_text": "This is a job that Jill, our AI Recruiter, is recruiting for on behalf of one of our customers.She will pick the best candidates from Jack's networkThe next step is to speak to Jack.Founding EngineerSalary: \u00a370k-\u00a3100k + EquityCompany Description: Getjelly.co.uk - Profitable AI startup backed by early investors in Revolut and Wise.Job Description:Join a high-velocity team building the operating system for the hospitality industry. As a Founding Engineer, you will leverage ML and AI to replace manual spreadsheets with automated workflows. You'll have direct ownership over product decisions, shipping code daily to thousands of users across 400+ locations to usher in a golden age of hospitality.Location: London, UKWhy this role is remarkable:Exceptional traction with a profitable business model and daily usage across hundreds of hospitality locations already established.Backed by elite angel investors who were early in fintech giants like Revolut, Wise, and Just Eat.True founding influence with significant equity and the ability to shape the technical culture of a fast-growing startup.What you will do:Architect and ship full-stack features using TypeScript across both frontend and backend production environments.Design and implement scalable relational database schemas and queries to handle complex kitchen management data without downtime.Collaborate directly with the founder and design team to turn messy operational problems into elegant, AI-driven software solutions.The ideal candidate:Possesses 4+ years of professional experience shipping and maintaining production-level software in a fast-paced environment.Demonstrates deep technical proficiency in TypeScript, software design patterns, and running live workloads on cloud providers.Maintains a product-focused mindset, prioritizing shipping to r